use we will assist you and your luggage when you land on the airport.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">3 fast track services at the airport:</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack when you arrive Vietnam airport: We welcome you at landing zone with a board with your name on it, then continue assisting you to complete all entry forms into Vietnam, including getting stamping without having to queue, keep your luggage in the separated area before the customs area and take you out of there as quickly as possible.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack at departure: We will greet you at the check-in area at Vietnam airport, then we&rsquo;ll assist you through the entry area and put you in the waiting area or departure area.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack between the flights: We will help you with fast track services between flights and stops</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The benefits of Vietnam Airport Fast track service</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The Fast Track Service package will meet all your requirements as well as expedite handling of all procedures, saving you a lot of time instead of waiting for entry procedures and customs clearance troubles. This service is available to all travelers of any airline. Whether you are a regular visitor or a business traveler, if you have any problems with immigration procedures, you are welcome to use our Vietnam Airport Fasttrack service</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The following customer groups are encouraged to use Vietnam Vip Airport Fast track service</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Those who enter Vietnam for the first time</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Those who need to quickly get the visa stamp </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">People who come to Vietnam with small children</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">People traveling in big groups</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Pregnant women</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">People with disabilities</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Great partner of the companies in Vietnam</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Foreigners hold important positions in Vietnamese businesses</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The process of Vietnam Airport Fast track service:</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The process does not take much time. After landing, please go to the visa area at the airport and contact our representative with your name board. Then you have to give us the essential documents at the airport and stamp cost. We will return your passport after every task is finished</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Detail steps</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Step 1:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Please contact our company through our hotline and provide details of your flight number, departure time and arrival time (International time + 7) or send request for service by email or phone and give us the information mentioned above. If you change your flight, please inform us 12 hours prior to your flight (except Saturdays, Sundays and public holidays).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Step 2: When your flight arrives in Vietnam, look for our representative, who will hold a board with your name on it..</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Step 3:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Give our staff your visa approval letter, immigration declaration, passport, 2 photos, and stamp cost ($ 25 / visitor for one entry visa and $ 50 for multiple entry visa valid for up to 3 months) for our staff to complete the entry procedures for guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Step 4:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Returning your passport with a stamped visa from our staff.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">With <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-airport-fasttrack-of-vietnamfasttrack\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam Airport Fast track service</strong></span></a>, the estimated time needed to finsish immigration procedures is about only 15 minutes. The process will go as normal if the passengers have no health problems or visa requirements at the airport.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Vietnam Airport Fast track service</strong> is the main service of our company. If you want to avoid wasting time and want to optimize the time you have, then let&rsquo;s book Vietnam Airport Fast track service when you come to Vietnam. Send us an email for more information about Vietnam Airport Fasttrack service at Vietnam airport. We can arrange a scheduled departure and arrival date to ensure that information is available at least 48 hours in advance.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Vietnam-Airport-Fasttrack.jpg', 0, 70, '', '2018-06-13 10:06:49', '2018-06-13 11:06:27', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam Airport Fasttrack of Vietnamfasttrack', 'Vietnamfasttrack Company Limited was one of the most reputable transporting companies. With more than 10 years of experience in serving thoudsands customers around the world, our company is confident to bring the best trips for you and your family. The company’s top service, Vietnam Airport Fasttrack, has built up our reputation as a pioneer in airport services.  ', 'vietnam-airport-fasttrack-of-vietnamfasttrack', ' Vietnam Airport Fasttrack', 1, ''),
(64, 'Vietnam Visa On Arrival', 'The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination’s aiport.  It’s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing Vietnam Visa on Arrival service for customers.\r\n', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination&rsquo;s aiport. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing<strong> <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Vietnam Visa on Arrival</span></a></strong><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"> </span></a>service for customers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">What is visa on arrival?</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa is a legal proof to certify that someone is allowed to enter or leave the country where the visa is issued. This permission may be in writing, or a page, a stamp affirmed in the passport... Visa has many types such as tourist visa, working visa ... with different terms and functions. Visa on Arrival, or Visa upon arrival, is a form of visa application for tourists. You don&rsquo;t need to apply in advance, instead you will be at the border of the country to complete entry procedures, and will pay a sum equivalent to the durations you will be staying in that country. To apply for a visa on arrival, travelers need to have an approval letter, usually provided by the traveler&rsquo;s travel agency</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa applications often take a long time to process and have lots of complex tasks, to the point it can make obtaining a visa difficult. If you are traveling on a regular basis, or if you need to travel overseas quickly for some reason, then <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam visa on arrival</strong></span></a> is the best option. &nbsp;It is also convenient for those who are away from the embassy or unexpectedly without a regular visa. The service will help you get entry visa at the airport without spending much time to apply for a visa before. This visa procedure is very simple, without costing much time and travel expenses. For this reason, Vietnam visa on arrival has become one of Vietnamfasttrack&rsquo;s main services. We provide this service to make travelers&rsquo; trip to Vietnam an easiest and most enjoyable experience.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa On Arrival application at Vietnamfasttrack Company</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam fasttrack will provide the visa approval letter, we are one of the company that was granted permission by the Immigration Department of Vietnam to provide the letter to customers before flying. Customers don&rsquo;t need to spend much time to register before flying; Vietnam fast track will ensure all procedures for visa on arrival. You only need to bring your visa approval letter to the airport to obtain a visa. If you want to check in at the airport faster and obtain your visa as soon as possible, you can book our Vietnam VIP fasttrack service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">What is the procedure for doing Visa On Arrival at Vietnamfasttrack?</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To book the Visa On Arrival at Vietnamfasttrack, customers need to provide:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- The original copy of the passport is still in use.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Return plane ticket.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Proof of hotel reservation.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Detailed schedule in Vietnam.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">After receiving the required documentation, Vietnamfasttrack will give customers the approval letter to fly to Vietnam. The type of visa normally applied for Visa On Arrival is a single entry visa. If you have multiple entry requirements and stay for longer periods of time, you can apply for multiple entry visas, 3 months entry or 3 months multiple entries. If you have any changes during your stay in Vietnam, you can also apply for a visa extension.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">There is no fixed standard for visa issuance. There are cases that fully meet the requirements of the embassy but still fail; or in many cases, not enough financial records or work can still be parked&hellip;Therefore, customers who want to travel should also prepare some things before applying for Visa:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Stable work, pay enough insurance.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Have solid financial foundation</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Passports are available for some &quot;entry&quot; seals of other countries, or passports of some countries with strong passports.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Clear travel schedule, invitations if any.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Extension of Vietnamese visas at Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Original passport valid for use.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Confirm to the local police station of where you stay.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Form N5 certified by the guarantee company in Vietnam.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Renewal period is 5 working days excluding weekends and holidays.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnamfasttrack Company are a prestigious visa service supplier with more than 10 years of experience in the field of visa support, tourism services&hellip;With a team of trained and commited professionals, we are ready to assist you 24/24 with the lowest cost and the highest guarantee. You can contact the Vietnamfasttrack company through our hotline or our website at any time to get support for <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-airport-fasttrack-of-vietnamfasttrack\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam visa on arrival</strong></span></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Vietnam-visa-on-arrival.jpg', 0, 69, '', '2018-06-13 10:06:34', '2018-06-13 11:06:34', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam Visa On Arrival', 'The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination’s aiport.  It’s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing Vietnam Visa on Arrival service for customers.\r\n', 'vietnam-visa-on-arrival', 'Vietnam visa on arrival', 1, ''),
(65, 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge Service', 'Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. The Vietnam VIP lounge service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.\r\n', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>The Vietnam VIP lounge</strong></span></a> service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Introduction about Vietnam VIP lounge Service of Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">With many years of experience &nbsp;in providing airport services, having served thousands of customers at international airports such as Noi Bai and Tan Son Nhat, Vietnamfasttrack realized that warm welcoming, fast airport procedures is the demand of many visitors, especially the businessmen</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">For that reason, Vietnamfasttrack has launched a new service for travelers: Vietnam VIP lounge service. We are proud to be one of the leading providers of <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam VIP lounge services</strong></span></a>. With high-class pickup service, our staff will pick you up at the gate of aircraft, the we offer private vip cars to transport yo from the plane to the VIP lounge. During the waiting process, guests will rest at the VIP lounge, while our staff at the border gate will complete the immigration procedures for you</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The biggest difference between a normal passenger and an Vietnamfasttrack VIP guest is the quality of the airport service and the personalized service. <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-vip-lounge-service\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam VIP lounge service</strong></span></a> has proved to be extremely useful during busy periods in the years like the holidays. The number of passengers increases significantly, therefore the waiting time for a passenger is much longer. Normally, passengers must take no less than 30 minutes to queue and complete all customs procedures before leaving the airport. Meanwhile, with Vietnam VIP lounge service, VIP guests will be picked up by staff at the elevator, have their customs clearance and entry completed at the private counters by our assistant, get their luggage ready. And all our VIP guests have to do is to wait and rest in the VIP lounge. The time needed to welcome and complete procedures for VIP service users is only from 10 to 15 minutes.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Not only bring guests convenience by being welcomed or farewell as a VIP, shorten the time for getting luggage, customs clearance, exit &ndash; entry procedure, Vietnam VIP lounge service provided by Vietnamfasttrack also satisfies customers with our friendly and professtional service, bringing the best trips for all kinds of customers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The process of Vietnam VIP lounge service</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1.1. Departure Flight </span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- When customers arrive at the airport, Vietnamfasttrack staffs will welcome guests at the hall of VIP A, VIP B and lead the guests to the VIP lounge and receive luggage and passport of guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Reception staff at VIP A, VIP B will serve VIP guests with tea, mineral water and fruit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Vietnamfasttrack staffs will complete the procedures such as checking air ticket, luggage, security checks, customs and stamped exit in the passport of the guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- 4-seat cars like Mercedes, Toyota Camry will take VIP passengers to private aircraft.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Special vehicles will carry your luggage to the aircraft.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Finish the service when the customers have got on the plane</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers note:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- This service allows up to 5 guest representatives to attend VIP A, VIP B and come to the plane at the airport.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1.2. Arrival Flight </span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- When the plane landed at the airport, Vietnamfasttrack staffs will pick up guests at the flight deck.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- 4-seat cars such as Mercedes, Toyota Camry will bring VIP passengers from the aircraft into the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Reception staff at VIP A, VIP B will serve VIP guests with tea, mineral water and fruit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Vietnamfasttrack staffs will do the procedures such as baggage handling, security checks, customs and stamped entry into the passport of guests and handed them over to guests at the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Fare guests and finish the service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers note:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- This service allows up to 5 delegates to welcome the delegation at the foot of the plane in the airport and VIP A, VIP B.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Our Vietnam VIP lounge service include</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- A uniformed assistant holding a signboard with your name on at the arrival gate</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- A car transporting you with our staff directly to the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- The airport procedures are completed by our staffs while you wait in the VIP lounge</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnamfasttrack is confident that our VIP lounge service can bring you the best experience at a Vietnam airport and satisfy all your needs. To book our service, you can go to our website for online booking or contact our hotline. We accept online payment by international credit card such as Visa Card and Master Card. </span></span></p>\r\n', 'Vietnam-VIP-lounge-service.jpg', 0, 71, '', '2018-06-13 10:06:09', '2018-06-26 07:06:56', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge Service', 'Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. The Vietnam VIP lounge service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.', 'vietnam-airport-vip-lounge-service', 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge service', 1, '');
INSERT INTO `news` (`news_id`, `news_name`, `news_des`, `news_content`, `news_img`, `news_views`, `newscat_id`, `news_author`, `news_created_date`, `news_update_date`, `state`, `news_sub_info1`, `news_sub_info2`, `news_sub_info3`, `news_sub_info4`, `news_sub_info5`, `title_seo`, `des_seo`, `friendly_url`, `keyword`, `created_id`, `newstag_arr`) VALUES
(66, 'Vietnam Airport Transfer Service From Vietnamfasttrack', 'Almost the airports in Vietnam are far from the city center, and at the same time, the airport transfer service at airports usually do not meet the guest’s requirements because there are usually taxi drivers who pick up the guests lately or charge unsuitable prices. Vietnamfasttrack provides Vietnam airport transfer service with reasonable price, dedicated service for you to use, contributing to a enjoyable and succesful trip for our customers.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Almost the airports in Vietnam are far from the city center, and at the same time, the airport transfer service at airports usually do not meet the guest&rsquo;s requirements because there are usually taxi drivers who pick up the guests lately or charge unsuitable prices. Vietnamfasttrack provides <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-airport-transfer-service-from-vietnamfasttrack\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam airport transfer service</strong></span></a> with reasonable price, dedicated service for you to use, contributing to a enjoyable and succesful trip for our customers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Overview of Vietnam airport transfer service by Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam airport transfer service</strong></span></a> is for both business and leisure travelers who want to arrange a trip to or from the airport in advance. It differs from normal taxi service by having high quality cars with highly skilled professional drivers who are fluent in English and possess wide knowledge of culture. Our service include:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Transportation from the airport to the city center and vice versa.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Transportation from the airport to the provinces and vice versa.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Transportation by tour</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Two-way Transportation between airport and hotel</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-vip-lounge-service\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam airport transfer service</strong></span></a> operates in less than 24 hours of every trip, is contracted according to the transportation way, and is charged in km, running time, standby time (reservation can be made before or immediately)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Currently Vietnam airport transfer service of Vietnamfasttrack is popular with some of the following vehicles:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&bull; Vietnam airport transfer service from 4 seats to 7 seats.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&bull; Vietnam airport transfer service 16 seats to 45 seats.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Why should you book Vietnam airport transfer service from Vietnamfasttrack?</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Absolute safety: For each reservation request, customers will be provided with information about the license plate number, driver&#39;s name + phone number of the driver. In addition, the customer is also updated with the contact details of the service provider. Thus, in case of forgetting the property, or not being happy about the service attitude of the driver, not satisfied with the quality of the car, the customer can absolutely contact the Executive Department to be supported in fastest time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Fixed payment amount: When confirming the reservation request, customers will be notified about the fee to be paid. In addition to the amount announced, customers will not have to pay any additional costs.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Convenience: Limitation of waiting time for passengers. Vehicles and drivers will be available at the airport (or hotel) to pick you up at the agreed time. For airport transfers, if the flight is late or if the passenger needs time to complete the customs formalities, the vehicle and driver will continue to wait and pick up passengers within a two-hour period. In this case, you can actively contact the driver to report the situation and ask the car to wait at the airport.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Benefit when customers use Vietnam airport transfer service of Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Pick up and meet the guests on time, at the location chosen by and most suitable for guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- You can choose from a wide variety of luxury cars ranging from medium to high-class on demand. Vietnamfasttrack owns more than 200 luxury cars, ranging from 4 to 45 seats with comfortable interior, modern like Mitsubishi Attrage, Ford Transit, Mercedes E-class, Mercedes S-class, Toyota Camry ... We have the vehicles to satify the demand for transportation and travel of various classes of passengers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Vietnamfasttrack understands that for any flight, time is the most important and should be top priority. The staff of Vietnamfasttrack will advise you the most suitable time to start the transportation, and our professional process ensure customers can optimize their time spent on the vehicles</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- At each airport, Vietnamfasttrack has its own service desk to assist customers. Staff will pick you up and guide you to the necessary procedures.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Coordinate the receipt and transportation of luggage in fastest time</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Professional customers service with 24/7 hotline support, and friendly and enthusiast staffs</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Drivers are recruited and trained professionally. In particular, they are able to communicate well in English, with enough international driver safety certificates.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Easy booking: Just go to our website, fill in the name, phone number, email, date and time, place of pick up and press to book the car. The staff of Vietnamfasttrack will quickly contact and advise the schedule as well as the best price list with each type of car for you to choose.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">This is one of the main services of Vietnamfasttrack. Vietnamfasttrack is constantly striving, aiming to bring passengers maximum convenience. Only by booking a service by telephone or online, when the passengers land on the Airport, they will be greeted by Vietnamfasttrack staffs. In addition, passengers will be served with cold towels, mineral water and take luggage to the waiting car.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">With the motto of putting the benefits of customers as our top priority, when using any service of Vietnamfasttrack, customers will be completely assured by the prestige and quality of our company. Vietnamfasttrack is confident in bringing you the best experience at Vietnam airport.</span></span></p>\r\n', 'Vietnam-airport-transfer-service.jpg', 0, 72, '', '2018-06-13 10:06:40', '2018-06-13 11:06:23', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 'Vietnam Airport Transfer Service From Vietnamfasttrack', 'Almost the airports in Vietnam are far from the city center, and at the same time, the airport transfer service at airports usually do not meet the guest’s requirements because there are usually taxi drivers who pick up the guests lately or charge unsuitable prices. Vietnamfasttrack provides Vietnam airport transfer service with reasonable price, dedicated service for you to use, contributing to a enjoyable and succesful trip for our customers.', 'vietnam-airport-transfer-service-from-vietnamfasttrack', 'Vietnam airport transfer service', 1, '');

