nd-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">第三个原因是，<a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/fast-track-service-in-ho-chi-minh-tan-son-nhat-airport\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#337ab7; text-decoration:none; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size:14px; vertical-align:baseline\"><strong>机场快速服务</strong>&nbsp;</a>有一个非常专业的，友好和热情的工作团队。我们当地的机场工作人员会在机场接你。他们会帮助你的程序，并帮助您拿行李了。我们的员工总是尽自己所能，给你与机场快速服务一个奇妙的经历</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">如何预订越南最顶级的机场快速通道服务？</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><img alt=\"机场快速通道服务\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.vietnamfasttrack.org/image/images/Airport-fast-track-service.jpg\" width=\"600\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">工作人员满足机场客户</span></span></span></em></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">该服务为任何行程的最佳选择。并与Vietnamfasttrack，领先的公司提供机场快速通道服务，它是很容易预订服务。所有你需要做的就是访问我们的网站或拨打我们的网站，以预订和体验最好的<a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/airport-fast-track-service-useful-choice-for-the-flights\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#337ab7; text-decoration:none; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size:14px; vertical-align:baseline\"><strong>机场快速轨道服务</strong></a>在越南。 &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Vietnamfasttrack公司是最有信誉的运输公司之一，提供机场快速通道服务，最高的质量。凭借超过10年的市场经营活动中，公司有信心将最好的旅行，为您和您的家人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'airport-fast-track-service-useful-choice-for-the-flights', 'Airport Fast Track Service - Useful Choice For The Flights ', 'Many people often not have a good experience when they arrive at airports in Vietnam, mostly because of long and tiring formality process. If you want to save your precious time,  Airport fast track service is a suitable solution for you. ', 'Airport fast track service'),
(123, 62, 'vn', 'Vietnamfasttrask And Services', 'Vietnamfasttrack company is one of the most reputable and quality companies in the market. We specialize in transporting people and goods, both at domestic and abroad. With a team of staffs and professional drivers that work over 10 years, our company is confident to bring the best service to everyone. ', '<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The services of Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">We provide services at airports for all types of travelers, who don&rsquo;t want to &nbsp;have to queue for many hours to complete airport procedures. If you have an upcoming meeting or any other reason that you are in a hurry, you could book the services of our company to be served as a VIP guest at all Vietnam international airports. The services provided by <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam fast-track</strong></span></a> help customers no longer have to worry at any international airport in Vietnam. With our range of services, customers can leave the airport early and will no longer have to wait in long lines, because we will assist you and your luggage when you arrive at the airport. Our system includes a welcome airside at the air bridge, fast track and assistance through visa and border control. Booking and reservation systems will help you select and book the service accurately. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/gioi-thieu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam fast-track</strong></span></a> works with the motto: react fast, start smoothly, and connect successfully. We specialize in providing two main types of services: Vietnam VIP airport fast-track, and Vietnam visa on arrival. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1. Vietnam VIP airport fasttrack</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam VIP airport fasttrack is the company&rsquo;s trademark service and the one that built our reputation as the leading company in airport services. Our staff will meet you at the air bridge. They will help you bypass the queue to check your visa or passport, escort you to the luggage area and customs. Before departure, they will contact your driver, assist you through booking and entry; and take you to the airline lounge and the port. Our strength lies in the fast, easy and professional process that help customers optimize their time at the airport, with high quality customer service, our will to provide service to all kinds of customers at a reasonable price</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">2. Vietnam visa on arrival</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Another main service of Vietnamfasttrack, Vietnam visa on arrival works in harmony with the VIP airport fasttrack service to help customers accomplish the airport procedures the quickest way possible. To enter any country, the first step is to apply for a visa of that country. The visa application procedure has to go through many steps and take a lot of time. Understanding how this can be an inconvenience for customers, Visa on arrival is designed by Vietnamfasttrack to be the best option for those who are away from the embassy, or in urgent need of a visa to enter the country. The Vietnam Visa on Arrival service helps you get your entry visa right at the airport. This visa procedure is very simple, it costs almost no time and travel expenses. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers do not have to apply for a visa before flying, but only need a Visa approval letter, provided by Vietnamfasttrack, and get a visa on arrival at the airport. Guests can obtain their own visa at the airport with this letter. If you want to get the visa right after landing, Vietnam fast-track provides Vietnam VIP airport fast track service to ensure your wish.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Besides, we have additional services to give customers the best experience with Vietnam airport transfer and Vietnam VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">3. Vietnam airport transfer</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Aside from airport procedures, another thing that often take a lot of time and tire out foreign customers when coming to Vietnam is finding a suitable transportation means to the hotel or their accomodation. That is the reason for our Vietnam airport transfer service. We provide a fast and convenient transportation service that is ready right after you step out of the airport. Our booking processors and booking service allow you to enter details of your trip, it will list a variety of vehicles for you to choose from. We provide a list of vehicles, including group travel prices for arrivals and departures from the airport to convention centers or hotels.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam airport transfer always uses new high quality vehicles, professional drivers who have been trained with English skills and cultural knowledge. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">4. Vietnam Airport VIP lounge</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A true feeling of comfort and luxury, the Vietnam VIP lounge serves to give you the best time at the airport. A private space when dropping a nap on a massage chair to prepare for a long flight; choose a menu that best suits you while enjoying the weather; using the Wi-Fi internet to work even before boarding a business center area is something your business is looking forward to.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">There is a VIP lounge at each international airport, our staff will come to the airport welcome guests, and then VIP facilities will transfer guests into the VIP lounge and complete procedures for guests. You will enjoy the VIP service while we help you complete the procedure. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Our values</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">We always strive to improve the quality of our services such as the selection of modern vehicles, easy and flexible booking, language training and cultural understanding for the drivers as well as the professionalism of the service staff, we are even willing to provide tour guides if you have a need. In the future, the company will become the famous brand in Vietnam and abroad, so the customers can trust the price and quality of our services.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">For over 10 years, Vietnam fast-track Company has assisted thousands of travelers over the airport. The fast track service applies to any traveler, on any airline brand, in any cabin class, and at all major airports. Our specialized staff will help you choose the most accurate service at the lowest cost. We always provide you with the best service, with special assistance to meet your needs at domestic and international airports.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'vietnamfasttrask-and-services', 'Vietnamfasttrask And Services', 'Vietnamfasttrack company is one of the most reputable and quality companies in the market. We specialize in transporting people and goods, both at domestic and abroad. With a team of staffs and professional drivers that work over 10 years, our company is confident to bring the best service to everyone. ', 'Vietnam Airport Fast-Track'),
