(127, 64, 'vn', 'Vietnam Visa On Arrival', 'The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination’s aiport.  It’s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing Vietnam Visa on Arrival service for customers.\r\n', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination&rsquo;s aiport. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing<strong> <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Vietnam Visa on Arrival</span></a></strong><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"> </span></a>service for customers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">What is visa on arrival?</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa is a legal proof to certify that someone is allowed to enter or leave the country where the visa is issued. This permission may be in writing, or a page, a stamp affirmed in the passport... Visa has many types such as tourist visa, working visa ... with different terms and functions. Visa on Arrival, or Visa upon arrival, is a form of visa application for tourists. You don&rsquo;t need to apply in advance, instead you will be at the border of the country to complete entry procedures, and will pay a sum equivalent to the durations you will be staying in that country. To apply for a visa on arrival, travelers need to have an approval letter, usually provided by the traveler&rsquo;s travel agency</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa applications often take a long time to process and have lots of complex tasks, to the point it can make obtaining a visa difficult. If you are traveling on a regular basis, or if you need to travel overseas quickly for some reason, then <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam visa on arrival</strong></span></a> is the best option. &nbsp;It is also convenient for those who are away from the embassy or unexpectedly without a regular visa. The service will help you get entry visa at the airport without spending much time to apply for a visa before. This visa procedure is very simple, without costing much time and travel expenses. For this reason, Vietnam visa on arrival has become one of Vietnamfasttrack&rsquo;s main services. We provide this service to make travelers&rsquo; trip to Vietnam an easiest and most enjoyable experience.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visa On Arrival application at Vietnamfasttrack Company</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnam fasttrack will provide the visa approval letter, we are one of the company that was granted permission by the Immigration Department of Vietnam to provide the letter to customers before flying. Customers don&rsquo;t need to spend much time to register before flying; Vietnam fast track will ensure all procedures for visa on arrival. You only need to bring your visa approval letter to the airport to obtain a visa. If you want to check in at the airport faster and obtain your visa as soon as possible, you can book our Vietnam VIP fasttrack service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">What is the procedure for doing Visa On Arrival at Vietnamfasttrack?</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To book the Visa On Arrival at Vietnamfasttrack, customers need to provide:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- The original copy of the passport is still in use.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Return plane ticket.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Proof of hotel reservation.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Detailed schedule in Vietnam.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">After receiving the required documentation, Vietnamfasttrack will give customers the approval letter to fly to Vietnam. The type of visa normally applied for Visa On Arrival is a single entry visa. If you have multiple entry requirements and stay for longer periods of time, you can apply for multiple entry visas, 3 months entry or 3 months multiple entries. If you have any changes during your stay in Vietnam, you can also apply for a visa extension.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">There is no fixed standard for visa issuance. There are cases that fully meet the requirements of the embassy but still fail; or in many cases, not enough financial records or work can still be parked&hellip;Therefore, customers who want to travel should also prepare some things before applying for Visa:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Stable work, pay enough insurance.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Have solid financial foundation</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Passports are available for some &quot;entry&quot; seals of other countries, or passports of some countries with strong passports.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Clear travel schedule, invitations if any.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Extension of Vietnamese visas at Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Original passport valid for use.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Confirm to the local police station of where you stay.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Form N5 certified by the guarantee company in Vietnam.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Renewal period is 5 working days excluding weekends and holidays.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnamfasttrack Company are a prestigious visa service supplier with more than 10 years of experience in the field of visa support, tourism services&hellip;With a team of trained and commited professionals, we are ready to assist you 24/24 with the lowest cost and the highest guarantee. You can contact the Vietnamfasttrack company through our hotline or our website at any time to get support for <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-airport-fasttrack-of-vietnamfasttrack\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam visa on arrival</strong></span></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'vietnam-visa-on-arrival', 'Vietnam Visa On Arrival', 'The term Visa On Arrival has become very popular with people who regularly travel abroad. It allows customers to skip the long and complex visa application at their home country and quickly receive their visa after landing at the destination’s aiport.  It’s a convenient service that has proved to be really useful for travelers to save time and simplify their procedures. In Vietnam, Vietnamfasttrack is the most trusted company in providing Vietnam Visa on Arrival service for customers.\r\n', 'Vietnam visa on arrival'),
