(129, 65, 'vn', 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge Service', 'Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. The Vietnam VIP lounge service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.\r\n', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>The Vietnam VIP lounge</strong></span></a> service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Introduction about Vietnam VIP lounge Service of Vietnamfasttrack</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">With many years of experience &nbsp;in providing airport services, having served thousands of customers at international airports such as Noi Bai and Tan Son Nhat, Vietnamfasttrack realized that warm welcoming, fast airport procedures is the demand of many visitors, especially the businessmen</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">For that reason, Vietnamfasttrack has launched a new service for travelers: Vietnam VIP lounge service. We are proud to be one of the leading providers of <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam VIP lounge services</strong></span></a>. With high-class pickup service, our staff will pick you up at the gate of aircraft, the we offer private vip cars to transport yo from the plane to the VIP lounge. During the waiting process, guests will rest at the VIP lounge, while our staff at the border gate will complete the immigration procedures for you</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The biggest difference between a normal passenger and an Vietnamfasttrack VIP guest is the quality of the airport service and the personalized service. <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-vip-lounge-service\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Vietnam VIP lounge service</strong></span></a> has proved to be extremely useful during busy periods in the years like the holidays. The number of passengers increases significantly, therefore the waiting time for a passenger is much longer. Normally, passengers must take no less than 30 minutes to queue and complete all customs procedures before leaving the airport. Meanwhile, with Vietnam VIP lounge service, VIP guests will be picked up by staff at the elevator, have their customs clearance and entry completed at the private counters by our assistant, get their luggage ready. And all our VIP guests have to do is to wait and rest in the VIP lounge. The time needed to welcome and complete procedures for VIP service users is only from 10 to 15 minutes.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Not only bring guests convenience by being welcomed or farewell as a VIP, shorten the time for getting luggage, customs clearance, exit &ndash; entry procedure, Vietnam VIP lounge service provided by Vietnamfasttrack also satisfies customers with our friendly and professtional service, bringing the best trips for all kinds of customers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The process of Vietnam VIP lounge service</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1.1. Departure Flight </span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- When customers arrive at the airport, Vietnamfasttrack staffs will welcome guests at the hall of VIP A, VIP B and lead the guests to the VIP lounge and receive luggage and passport of guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Reception staff at VIP A, VIP B will serve VIP guests with tea, mineral water and fruit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Vietnamfasttrack staffs will complete the procedures such as checking air ticket, luggage, security checks, customs and stamped exit in the passport of the guests.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- 4-seat cars like Mercedes, Toyota Camry will take VIP passengers to private aircraft.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Special vehicles will carry your luggage to the aircraft.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Finish the service when the customers have got on the plane</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers note:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- This service allows up to 5 guest representatives to attend VIP A, VIP B and come to the plane at the airport.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1.2. Arrival Flight </span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- When the plane landed at the airport, Vietnamfasttrack staffs will pick up guests at the flight deck.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- 4-seat cars such as Mercedes, Toyota Camry will bring VIP passengers from the aircraft into the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Reception staff at VIP A, VIP B will serve VIP guests with tea, mineral water and fruit.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Vietnamfasttrack staffs will do the procedures such as baggage handling, security checks, customs and stamped entry into the passport of guests and handed them over to guests at the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- Fare guests and finish the service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers note:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- This service allows up to 5 delegates to welcome the delegation at the foot of the plane in the airport and VIP A, VIP B.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Our Vietnam VIP lounge service include</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- A uniformed assistant holding a signboard with your name on at the arrival gate</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- A car transporting you with our staff directly to the VIP lounge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">- The airport procedures are completed by our staffs while you wait in the VIP lounge</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Vietnamfasttrack is confident that our VIP lounge service can bring you the best experience at a Vietnam airport and satisfy all your needs. To book our service, you can go to our website for online booking or contact our hotline. We accept online payment by international credit card such as Visa Card and Master Card. </span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'vietnam-airport-vip-lounge-service', 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge Service', 'Welcoming guests at the door of the aircraft, guiding guests to VIP lounge while we go through the immigration procedures, customs procedures at the private counters, take luggage in advance and transfer outside in advance,.. The Vietnam VIP lounge service is a new high class service for passengers at Vietnamese international airports provided by Vietnamfasttrack company. Passengers can take the full advantage of this service by booking it in accompany with the Vietnam Vip Airport Fasttrack Service.', 'Vietnam Airport VIP lounge service'),
(130, 65, 'en', '越南机场贵宾休息室服务', '我们在飞机门口欢迎客人，引导客人到贵宾休息室，同时我们办理入境手续，在私人柜台办理海关手续，提前收取行李并提前转机，..越南贵宾休息室服务是一个新的高度 越南国际机场为Vietnamfasttrack公司提供的乘客服务。 乘客可以在越南Vip机场快速列车服务的同时预订，充分利用这项服务。', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">在飞机门口欢迎客人，引导客人到贵宾休息室，而我们经过入境手续，在私人柜台办理海关手续，取行李事先并提前转移之外，..&nbsp;<a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/dich-vu\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#337ab7; text-decoration:none; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size:14px; vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>越南贵宾休息室</strong></span></span></a>服务的新高一流的服务在由Vietnamfasttrack公司提供的越南国际机场的乘客。乘客可通过预订它与越南的机场贵宾服务的FastTrack陪采取充分利用这项服务。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">关于Vietnamfasttrack的越南贵宾休息室服务介绍</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">随着提供机场服务，在国际机场，如内排和新山一曾担任数千名客户的多年经验，Vietnamfasttrack意识到热烈欢迎，机场快程序是许多游客的需求，尤其是商人</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">出于这个原因，Vietnamfasttrack已经推出了旅客的新服务：越南贵宾休息室服务。我们很自豪能成为领先的供应商之一，<a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-visa-on-arrival\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#337ab7; text-decoration:none; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size:14px; vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>越南贵宾休息室服务</strong></span></span></a>。随着高档皮卡的服务，我们的工作人员会去接你在飞机的门，我们提供私人贵宾车从飞机上运哟贵宾休息室。在等待过程中，客人休息的贵宾休息室，而我们在关闸的工作人员会为您完成入境手续</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"font-family:Raleway,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">一个正常的乘客和Vietnamfasttrack贵宾之间最大的区别是在机场的服务和个性化服务的质量。<a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/vietnam-vip-lounge-service\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box; color:#337ab7; text-decoration:none; margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; font-size:14px; vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>越南贵宾休息室服务</strong></span></span></a>已被证明是在在岁月像假期繁忙时段是非常有用的。乘客人数显著增加，因此对于乘客的等待时间要长得多。通常情况下，乘客必须拿不下30分钟，排队和离开机场前完成所有通关手续。同时，与越南贵宾休息室服务，贵宾将由工作人员在电梯回升，有自己的清关和入境在我们的助理私人柜台完成，拿到自己的行李准备。我们所有的VIP客人需要做的就是等待和休息的贵宾休息室。所需要的时间欢迎和VIP服务用户手续齐全仅仅是从10到15分钟。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">