(83, 59, 'vn', 'ABOUT US', 'Vietnamfasttrack company is one of the most reputable and quality companies in the market. We specialize in transporting people and goods, both at domestic and abroad. With a team of staffs and professional drivers that work over 10 years, our company is confident to bring the best service to everyone. ', '<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>The services of Vietnamfasttrack</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We provide services at airports for all types of travelers, who don&rsquo;t want to &nbsp;have to queue for many hours to complete airport procedures. If you have an upcoming meeting or any other reason that you are in a hurry, you could book the services of our company to be served as a VIP guest at all Vietnam international airports. The services provided by <a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/\"><strong>Vietnam fast-track</strong></a> help customers no longer have to worry at any international airport in Vietnam. With our range of services, customers can leave the airport early and will no longer have to wait in long lines, because we will assist you and your luggage when you arrive at the airport. Our system includes a welcome airside at the air bridge, fast track and assistance through visa and border control. Booking and reservation systems will help you select and book the service accurately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><a href=\"http://vietnamfasttrack.org/gioi-thieu\"><strong>Vietnam fast-track</strong></a> works with the motto: react fast, start smoothly, and connect successfully. We specialize in providing two main types of services: Vietnam VIP airport fast-track, and Vietnam visa on arrival.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>1 Vietnam VIP airport fasttrack</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Vietnam VIP airport fasttrack is the company&rsquo;s trademark service and the one that built our reputation as the leading company in airport services. Our staff will meet you at the air bridge. They will help you bypass the queue to check your visa or passport, escort you to the luggage area and customs. Before departure, they will contact your driver, assist you through booking and entry; and take you to the airline lounge and the port. Our strength lies in the fast, easy and professional process that help customers optimize their time at the airport, with high quality customer service, our will to provide service to all kinds of customers at a reasonable price</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>2. Vietnam visa on arrival</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Another main service of Vietnamfasttrack, Vietnam visa on arrival works in harmony with the VIP airport fasttrack service to help customers accomplish the airport procedures the quickest way possible. To enter any country, the first step is to apply for a visa of that country. The visa application procedure has to go through many steps and take a lot of time. Understanding how this can be an inconvenience for customers, Visa on arrival is designed by Vietnamfasttrack to be the best option for those who are away from the embassy, or in urgent need of a visa to enter the country. The Vietnam Visa on Arrival service helps you get your entry visa right at the airport. This visa procedure is very simple, it costs almost no time and travel expenses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Customers do not have to apply for a visa before flying, but only need a Visa approval letter, provided by Vietnamfasttrack, and get a visa on arrival at the airport. Guests can obtain their own visa at the airport with this letter. If you want to get the visa right after landing, Vietnam fast-track provides Vietnam VIP airport fast track service to ensure your wish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Besides, we have additional services to give customers the best experience with Vietnam airport transfer and Vietnam VIP lounge.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>3. Vietnam airport transfer</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aside from airport procedures, another thing that often take a lot of time and tire out foreign customers when coming to Vietnam is finding a suitable transportation means to the hotel or their accomodation. That is the reason for our Vietnam airport transfer service. We provide a fast and convenient transportation service that is ready right after you step out of the airport. Our booking processors and booking service allow you to enter details of your trip, it will list a variety of vehicles for you to choose from. We provide a list of vehicles, including group travel prices for arrivals and departures from the airport to convention centers or hotels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Vietnam airport transfer always uses new high quality vehicles, professional drivers who have been trained with English skills and cultural knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>4. Vietnam VIP lounge</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">A true feeling of comfort and luxury, the Vietnam VIP lounge serves to give you the best time at the airport. A private space when dropping a nap on a massage chair to prepare for a long flight; choose a menu that best suits you while enjoying the weather; using the Wi-Fi internet to work even before boarding a business center area is something your business is looking forward to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">There is a VIP lounge at each international airport, our staff will come to the airport welcome guests, and then VIP facilities will transfer guests into the VIP lounge and complete procedures for guests. You will enjoy the VIP service while we help you complete the procedure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Our values</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We always strive to improve the quality of our services such as the selection of modern vehicles, easy and flexible booking, language training and cultural understanding for the drivers as well as the professionalism of the service staff, we are even willing to provide tour guides if you have a need. In the future, the company will become the famous brand in Vietnam and abroad, so the customers can trust the price and quality of our services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For over 10 years, Vietnam fast-track Company has assisted thousands of travelers over the airport. The fast track service applies to any traveler, on any airline brand, in any cabin class, and at all major airports. Our specialized staff will help you choose the most accurate service at the lowest cost. We always provide you with the best service, with special assistance to meet your needs at domestic and international airports.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'about-us', 'About Us', 'Vietnam Airport Fast-Track', 'Vietnamfasttrack company is one of the most reputable and quality companies in the market. We specialize in transporting people and goods, both at domestic and abroad. With a team of staffs and professional drivers that work over 10 years, our company is confident to bring the best service to everyone. '),
(84, 59, 'en', '关于我们', 'Vietnamfasttrack公司是市场上最有信誉和最优质的公司之一。 我们专注于运输国内外的人员和货物。 我们公司拥有一支员工和专业司机，工作超过10年，有信心为每个人提供最好的服务。', '<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align:start\"><strong>越南快速通道的服务</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">我们在机场为各种各样的旅客提供服务，他们不想为了完成机场手续而排几个小时的队。如果你有一个即将到来的会议或任何其他你着急的原因，你可以预订我们公司的服务作为VIP客人在所有越南国际机场。越南快速通道提供的服务帮助客户不再担心在越南的任何国际机场。有了我们的服务范围，顾客可以提前离开机场，不用再排长队等待，因为当你到达机场时，我们会帮助你和你的行李。我们的系统包括在空中大桥的欢迎机场，快速通道和通过签证和边境控制的协助。预订和预订系统将帮助您准确选择和预订服务。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ldquo;越南快速通道&rdquo;的口号是:快速反应，平稳启动，成功连接。我们专门提供两种主要的服务:越南贵宾机场快速通道和越南落地签证。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">越南VIP机场快速通道</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">越南VIP机场快速通道是公司的商标服务，是我们在机场服务领域的领先企业。我们的工作人员将在空中桥接你。他们会帮你绕过排队检查你的签证或护照，护送你到行李区和海关。出发前，他们会联系你的司机，协助你预订和入境;然后带你去候机室和港口。我们的优势在于快速、便捷、专业的流程，帮助客户优化在机场的时间，以优质的客户服务，我们将以合理的价格为各类客户提供服务</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>2. 越南落地签证</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">越南快轨公司的另一项主要服务是越南落地签证(Vietnamfasttrack)，该公司与VIP机场快轨公司(airport fasttrack)合作，帮助客户以最快的速度完成机场手续。要进入任何国家，第一步是申请该国的签证。签证申请程序要经过很多步骤，而且要花很多时间。了解到这一点会给客户带来不便，越南快速通道(Vietnamfasttrack)设计的&ldquo;落地签证&rdquo;(Visa on - arrival)是那些远离大使馆或急需签证入境的人的最佳选择。越南落地签证服务帮助你在机场拿到入境签证。这个签证程序非常简单，几乎不需要花费时间和旅费。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">乘客不需要在飞行前申请签证，只需要一份越南快速通道提供的签证批准书，并在抵达机场时获得签证。通过这封信，客人可以在机场获得自己的签证。如果您想在落地后立即获得签证，&ldquo;越南快车道&rdquo;为您提供&ldquo;越南VIP机场快车道&rdquo;服务。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">此外，我们还提供额外的服务，为客户提供最佳的体验越南机场中转和越南贵宾休息室。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>3.所示。越南机场转移</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">除了办理机场手续外，另一件常常需要花费大量时间、让外国客户在来越南时感到疲惫的事情，就是找到一种合适的交通方式去酒店或他们的住所。这就是我们提供越南机场中转服务的原因。我们提供快捷方便的运输服务，您一走出机场就可以享受到。我们的预订处理程序和预订服务允许您输入您的旅行详细信息，它将列出各种车辆供您选择。我们提供了车辆清单，包括从机场到会议中心或酒店的往返团体旅行价格。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">越南机场接送一直使用新型的高质量车辆，专业司机受过英语技能和文化知识的培训。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>4.所示。越南贵宾室</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">一个真正的感觉舒适和豪华，越南贵宾休息室为您提供最好的时间在机场。在按摩椅上打盹准备长途飞行时的私人空间;在享受天气的同时，选择最适合你的菜单;使用Wi-Fi互联网工作甚至在登机前商务中心区域是你的企业期待的事情。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">每个国际机场都有一个VIP休息室，我们的工作人员会到机场迎接客人，然后VIP设施会将客人转到VIP休息室，为客人办理完手续。在我们为您办理手续的同时，您将享受贵宾服务。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">我们的价值观</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">我们总是努力提高我们的服务质量,如现代车辆的选择,简单和灵活的预订,语言培训和文化理解的司机以及服务人员的专业性,我们甚至愿意提供导游如果你有需要。未来，公司将成为越南及海外的知名品牌，客户可以信赖我们的价格和服务质量。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">10多年来，越南快速通道公司一直在机场为数千名旅客提供帮助。快速通道服务适用于任何旅客，任何航空品牌，任何舱位级别，以及所有主要机场。我们的专业人员将帮助您以最低的成本选择最准确的服务。我们始终为您提供最优质的服务，为您在国内和国际机场的需求提供特殊的帮助。</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">机场快速通道和签证服务 - 高级服务为您提供最愉快的旅程</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'about-us', '关于我们', '', '');

